Relationship Between Physical Function and Health Utility in Patients Undergoing 
Surgical Treatment for Malignant Pleural Mesothelioma.

Tanaka T(1), Morishita S(2)(3), Hashimoto M(3), Nakamichi T(3), Uchiyama Y(3), 
