Rational Remodeling of Atypical Scaffolds for the Design of Photoswitchable 
Cannabinoid Receptor Tools.

Hu T(1)(2)(3), Zheng G(1), Xue D(1), Zhao S(1), Li F(1), Zhou F(1), Zhao F(1), 
Xie L(1)(2), Tian C(1), Hua T(1)(2), Zhao S(1)(2), Xu Y(1), Zhong G(1)(2), Liu 
ZJ(1)(2), Makriyannis A(4), Stevens RC(1)(2)(5), Tao H(1).

Author information:
(1)iHuman Institute, ShanghaiTech University, Pudong, Shanghai 201210, China.
(2)School of Life Science and Technology, ShanghaiTech University, Pudong, 
Shanghai 201210, China.
(3)CAS Center for Excellence in Molecular Cell Science, Shanghai Institute of 
Biochemistry and Cell Biology, University of Chinese Academy of Sciences, 
Beijing 100049, China.
(4)Center for Drug Discovery, Department of Pharmaceutical Sciences and 
Department of Chemistry and Chemical Biology, Northeastern University, Boston, 
